{
  "stem": "2522.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have a very interesting collection of documents-- which I donated to the-- to the Holocaust Museum, which, in my opinion, is a very, very unique set of documents-- which I collected after the war in Slovakia, which shows the incrementality of the laws and the degradation and the taking away of Jewish privileges and rights.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and it shows how the Slovak State, in some respect-- the way the Germans did it except not as brutally-- used a legal process by passing a law saying, well, there can be no Jewish innkeepers.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, by-- in six months, everybody who is a Jewish innkeeper has to give up their license and hand it over to what's called an 'arizator,' somebody who makes it Aryan, OK.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now you take the economic base of the innkeepers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, half of my uncles were innkeepers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, so that happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then, of course, the war scales up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "England enters the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody else enters the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The BBC makes broadcast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then that happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then you pass another law.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are certain streets where Jews cannot live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if it's a prominent merchant street, you cannot live on that street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the law that has been passed by the Slovak parliament shows the towns and the names of the street in the law.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It says, on Via [NON-ENGLISH], no Jew can live.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, they picked all the prominent Jewish places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- OK, so in 1940, we have to move out of the house my father built.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very traumatic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Required by law.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, you didn't sell the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't sell the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to give it to-- into a custody of an Aryan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- in other words, it was taken over.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
